description:
Wednesday August 13, 2008.

Alex welcomes Austin police chief Art Acevedo to the studio and also talks with Constitution Party presidential nominee Chuck Baldwin.  Jason Bermas joins to discuss his new movie Fabled Enemies.  Alex also announces the winners of the first video competitions he launched last week.

Sourced from the Infowars live stream and/or the podcast.  Includes content during commercials.  Commercial editing done by hand with volume correction on the low/high guests.  Four hours duration before commercial edit takes it to just over three hours of playing time.  
